作本日甲機關以優惠承購價格購入機械及設備之分錄。）（10分）', '[]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:32:00+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "ca304502c292", "answer_pdf_sha1": null, "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "112090", "c": "326", "s": "1109", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "甲、申論題部分", "subject": "政府會計", "year": "112", "exam_name": "112年公務人員高等考試三級考試暨普通考試", "original_question_number": "一", "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "heelevel3", "civil_category": "會計"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('heelevel3-d0d1b9a2-moex-00289', 'heelevel3-d0d1b9a2', 'heelevel3-d0d1b9a2-moex-112-ac2adf20', 'sub-heelevel3-d0d1b9a2-02', NULL, 'essay', '甲機關於X1年1月1日與A公司達成協議，甲機關以其持有的機械及設備交
